# Semgrep ignore patterns. Same gitignore syntax.

# aws-setup/ is the singleton operator-only Terraform stack: GitHub Actions OIDC role,
# CloudFront/Lambda@Edge for the BFF, ACM, Route53. The IAM policies on the OIDC role
# deliberately include role-management actions (Create/Update/Delete) scoped to
# `ai-website-agency-*` resources so per-PR deploy/destroy can manage Lambda exec roles.
# Semgrep's terraform.lang.security.iam priv-esc / resource-exposure rules flag these
# as exposure even with the Resource restriction — false positives for our use case.
aws-setup/
